response.original_title: Maanam: Koncert Maanam i Goście (25-lecie zespołu)
response.overview: In 2000 Maanam played live at Kongresowa Hall in Warsaw to celebrate the band's 25th anniversary. Many guests appeared on stage: Milo Kurtis, John Porter, Robert Brylewski, Zbigniew Namysłowski, Sławek Wierzcholski, Muniek Staszczyk, Justyna Steczkowska, Kasia Nosowska, Artur Rojek, Stanisław Soyka, Bogusław Łyszkiewicz. The concert was released the following year as the band's first concert DVD.
response.title: Maanam: Koncert Maanam i Goście (25-lecie zespołu)
